<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #ffc107;
        color: #333;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
        background: #f9f9f9;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        background-color: #0d6efd;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #666;
        font-size: 12px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Your Ad Has Been Rejected</h1>
      </div>
      
      <div class="content">
        <p>Dear <%= @user.email %>,</p>
        
        <p>We regret to inform you that your ad "<strong><%= @product.name %></strong>" has been rejected by our admin team.</p>
        
        <h3>Ad Details:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Title:</strong> <%= @product.name %></li>
          <li><strong>Category:</strong> <%= @product.category.name rescue "N/A" %></li>
          <li><strong>Price:</strong> Rs <%= number_with_delimiter(@product.price) %></li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>Common reasons for rejection include:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Incomplete or inaccurate information</li>
          <li>Poor quality or missing images</li>
          <li>Violation of our terms of service</li>
          <li>Inappropriate content</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply directly to this email.</p>
        <p>Â© <%= Time.current.year %> Livestock. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html> 